3.10	Chaser_(video_game)	Chaser (video game)	Chaser is a first-person shooter action video game developed by Cauldron. The game is built on the CloakNT 3D engine. Unlike many contemporary science fiction first-person shooters like Halo: Combat Evolved, Pariah, WarPath, and Unreal Tournament 2004, Chaser's weapons fire modern day projectiles.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/a/af/Chaser_Coverart.png
